-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4674_0.29.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-01T12:58:23" id="_1ba83061-9d84-49ca-b993-9b6570026006" type="insert"><num/><title id="_bdd499c5-b878-4c2c-8090-9c024b02c7f7"/></image-reference><callout id="_788fd9d2-d2a7-460a-93ee-7f8fe1849217"><callout-type ncc-info-type="notes"/><p>Where a shower is above a bath or spa, use requirements for shower.</p></callout></clause>